# NORYPT TAC database — curated, brand- and region-tagged.
# Format: <8-digit-tac> <brand> <region>
# Brands:  apple samsung xiaomi motorola
# Regions: na eu asia latam global
#
# Region tagging is best-effort. Manufacturers file separate TACs per
# launch region; only a subset of those mappings is publicly documented.
# TACs whose launch region is uncertain land in 'global' and match every
# region. Lines starting with '#' and blank lines are ignored.

